com.mweslacey.city.foodfail.fragment

Class FacilityDetailFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mweslacey.city.foodfail.fragment.FacilityDetailFragment

  • public class FacilityDetailFragment
extends Object
    Detail View for user-selected facility. FacilityDetailFragment is attached to MainActivity after user selects a facility from the list generated in the SearchFragment. This View displays a Google Map showing the location of the previously selected facility.
